model.name: Lv Beaubourg Ankle Boot
model.disambiguatingDescription: Reinterpreting one of Louis Vuitton's emblematic styles, the LV Beaubourg ankle boot in calf leather draws inspiration from combat boots with its lace-up design and rubber tip. A padded lining in Monogram nylon offers instant warmth and comfort. This model is characterized by its chunky yet lightweight outsole in micro and leather, which is complemented by white stitching.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Black
  • Calf leather
  • Monogram-nylon lining
  • Micro and leather outsole
  • 4 cm / 1.6-inch heel
  • Louis Vuitton-embossed leather tag
  • LV Initials insert in the heel
  • Made in Italy
